<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c1">" ضعيف"</span>. <span class="c1">"المنتبه"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٦٥٨)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
